    "Id": 4,
    "Content": "\n### Serenity 原版战绩（美股）\n\n| 标的 | 代码 | 涨幅 | 卡脖子定位 |\n|------|------|------|-----------|\n| AXT Inc | AXTI.US | +525%（YTD） | InP 衬底全球唯三产商 |\n| Applied Optoelectronics | AAOI.US | +348%（YTD） | CPO 激光器主力供应商 |\n| Sivers Semiconductors | SIVE.SE | — | CPO 激光器 + 硅光子 |\n| X-FAB | XFAB.EU | — | 特色工艺晶圆代工 |\n\n---\n\n## 六步分析链路\n\n| 步骤 | 核心问题 | 产出 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| 1️⃣ 定位板块周期 | 需求爆发 / 技术跃迁 / 供给受限？ | 板块所处阶段 |\n| 2️⃣ 溯源供应链 | 瓶颈在哪一层？ | 供应链层级图 |\n| 3️⃣ 找 A 股标的 | 哪些公司卡在这个节点？ | 四维信号卡 |\n| 4️⃣ 真伪筛选 | 哪些是\"真瓶颈\"，哪些是蹭热点？ | 筛选结论 |\n| 5️⃣ 多空确认 | 做多信号 vs 做空信号？ | 信号对照表 |\n| 6️⃣ 输出报告 | 含操作建议 + 风险提示 | 结构化报告 |\n\n---\n\n## 适用板块示例\n\n电力、光模块/CPO、半导体设备、军工、新能源车、医疗器械、创新药、农药、OLED……**任意 A 股板块均可分析**。\n\n| 板块 | 卡脖子节点 | 代表标的 |\n|------|-----------|---------|\n| **电力** | 特高压换流变压器 / 智能调度 | 国电南瑞(600406)、特变电工(600089) |\n| **光模块/CPO** | EAM 激光器 / MPO 连接器 | 源杰科技(688498)、炬光科技(688167) |\n| **半导体设备** | 薄膜沉积 / 光刻机核心零部件 | 中微公司(688012)、北方华创(002371) |\n| **军工** | 特种合金 / 高端复合材料 | 中简科技(300777)、光威复材(300699) |\n| **新能源车** | 碳纳米管导电剂 / 固态电池材料 | 天奈科技(688116)、当升科技(300073) |\n\n---\n\n## 快速开始",
    "ContentSha": "qzP4CyrwJberTJKJfEkHKt4qnNPPRde4Nbmyz9m+Fi4=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n### Serenity Original Track Record (US Stocks)\n\n| Target | Code | Increase | Choke Point Positioning |\n|--------|------|----------|------------------------|\n| AXT Inc | AXTI.US | +525% (YTD) | One of the world's three InP substrate manufacturers |\n| Applied Optoelectronics | AAOI.US | +348% (YTD) | Main supplier of CPO lasers |\n| Sivers Semiconductors | SIVE.SE | — | CPO lasers + silicon photonics |\n| X-FAB | XFAB.EU | — | Specialty process wafer foundry |\n\n---\n\n## Six-Step Analysis Chain\n\n| Step | Core Question | Output |\n|------|---------------|--------|\n| 1️⃣ Position sector cycle | Demand surge / technological leap / supply constraint? | Stage of the sector |\n| 2️⃣ Trace supply chain | Where is the bottleneck? | Supply chain hierarchy map |\n| 3️⃣ Find A-share targets | Which companies are stuck at this node? | Four-dimensional signal map |\n| 4️⃣ Authenticity screening | Which are the \"real bottlenecks\", which are hype? | Screening conclusions |\n| 5️⃣ Long-short confirmation | Long signals vs short signals? | Signal comparison table |\n| 6️⃣ Output report | Including operation suggestions + risk warnings | Structured report |\n\n---\n\n## Applicable Sector Examples\n\nPower, optical modules/CPO, semiconductor equipment, military industry, new energy vehicles, medical devices, innovative drugs, pesticides, OLED... **any A-share sector can be analyzed**.\n\n| Sector | Choke Point Node | Representative Targets |\n|--------|-----------------|-----------------------|\n| **Power** | UHV converter transformer / intelligent dispatch | Guodian Nari (600406), Tebian Electric Apparatus (600089) |\n| **Optical Modules/CPO** | EAM laser / MPO connector | Yuanjie Technology (688498), Juguang Technology (688167) |\n| **Semiconductor Equipment** | Thin film deposition / core parts of lithography machines | Zhongwei Company (688012), North Huachuang (002371) |\n| **Military Industry** | Special alloys / high-end composite materials | Zhongjian Technology (300777), Guangwei Composite (300699) |\n| **New Energy Vehicles** | Carbon nanotube conductive agent / solid-state battery materials | Tiannai Technology (688116), Dangsheng Technology (300073) |\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start",
